        <p>With a plan in place, we started designing and developing the first version of the app. Designers honed in on visual styling and user experience, while developers laid the foundation for the backend functionality. After a few weeks, we had a real, working app! We identified a rollout plan for our first release, and when we were ready, we loaded our app on a few tablets and gave them to designated Green Line officials to use. And the MBTA team has been collecting feedback and iterating on it ever since!</p>
